Package: ax10-luci
Version: 1.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Lee Chantrey <lchantrey@gmail.com>
Section: net
Priority: optional
Depends: ax10-svc, ax10-wifi
Description: Modern LuCI 21.02 web UI for the TP-Link Archer AX10, running a cross-built 19.07 rpcd + uhttpd on the firmware's 2013 ubusd. Serves the web GUI on :8080. rpcd and uhttpd are supervised by init-respawn via ax10-svc (this retires the webwatch keep-alive). Depends on ax10-wifi so the wireless page can actually apply changes.
